enbach]] |- |94 ||''[[Aruanda]]'' ||1960 ||{{Hs|Noronha}}[[Linduarte Noronha]] |- |95 ||''[[Carandiru (film)|Carandiru]]'' ||2003 ||{{Hs|Babenco}}[[Hector Babenco]] |- |96 ||''[[Blá Blá Blá]]'' ||1968 ||{{Hs|Tonacci}}[[Andrea Tonacci]] |- |97 ||''[[O Signo do Caos]]'' ||2003 ||{{Hs|Sganzerla}}[[Rogério Sganzerla]] |- |98 ||''[[The Year My Parents Went on Vacation]]'' ||2006 ||{{Hs|Hamburger}}[[Cao Hamburger]] |- |99 ||''[[Meteorango Kid, Herói Intergaláctico]]'' ||1969 ||{{Hs|Oliveira}}[[Andre Luis Oliveira]] |- |100 ||''[[Guerra Conjugal]]''/''[[Bar Esperanza]]'' ||1975/1983 ||{{Hs|Andrade/Carvana}}[[Joaquim Pedro de Andrade]]/[[Hugo Carvana]] |}
